== Server Deploy ==
There are known bugs requiring these commands to be ran several times rather than once.
=== hlds ===
{{cmd|prompt=steam ~
|./steamcmd/steamcmd.sh +login anonymous +force_install_dir "/home/steam/hlds/" +app_set_config 90 +app_update 90 validate +quit}}
=== cstrike ===
{{cmd|prompt=steam ~
|./steamcmd/steamcmd.sh +login anonymous +force_install_dir "/home/steam/cstrike/" +app_set_config 90 mod cstrike +app_update 90 mod cstrike validate +quit}}

== server ==
=== hlds ===
{{cmd|prompt=steam ~/hlds/
|./hlds_run +maxplayers 32}}
=== cstrike ===
{{cmd|prompt=steam ~/cstrike/
|./hlds_run -game cstrike -autoupdate +maxplayers 32 +map de_dust2}}

